section.section:
If the prior owner does not exercise the rights conferred by this subsection, the Department shall dispose of the interest in land through public sale, taking into account the following factors:
The full recovery of any expenditures from the State Hazardous Substance Control Fund;
To the extent practicable, the sale of the interest in land shall be at the fair market value;
The effect of the sale on surrounding land values or uses; and
The potential for public use of the interest in land by another public agency.
